msgid ""
"Settings for handling login via local accounts can be set by going to "
":menuselection:`System --> Access --> Servers`, then clicking the 'Edit' "
"icon (a pencil) for 'Local Database'. Here, you can improve security of "
"local user accounts by setting password length and complexity "
"constraints."
